spells.description:
Equip: Upon entering combat, and every 60 sec, gain either Massive or Miniature for 30 sec.

Miniature
Reduces your size by 20%, and increases your Speed by 1,152 and Haste by 7,718.

Massive
Increases your size by 20%, maximum health by 269,103, and Agility by 6,866.

Equip: Your abilities have a high chance to summon a phantom ethereal, dealing 201,465 Shadow damage to your target and 18,131 Shadow damage to all other enemies caught in its path. 

If the target is below 35% health, this effect summons two additional phantoms at 25% effectiveness.

effects.display_string: (2) Set: Void Reaper's Contract always summons additional phantoms against enemies afflicted by Queensbane.
